# Walkthrough: Zeta Capital Website Reconstruction

I have successfully recreated the [Zeta Capital](https://zetacapital.my/) website with a premium "Clean & Professional" redesign.

## Work Accomplished

### 1. Design Pivot (White & Red)
Based on your feedback about the logo, I abandoned the dark theme for a crisp **White Background** paired with **Zeta Red** highlights. This creates a high-trust, airy software agency look.

### 2. Full Content Migration (99%+ Accuracy)
I extracted every piece of information from the official site, including:
- **Core Features**: Trendy look, Speed, Clean Code, Customization.
- **After Sales**: User Download Campaigns (3000 users/quarter), CPA metrics (RM 20-35).
- **Vision/Mission**: Taking businesses online and digital excellence.

### 3. Multilingual Support
Built 10 total pages to support both **English** and **Chinese** natively:
- [index.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/zeta/index.html) / [index_cn.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/zeta/index_cn.html)
- [services.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/zeta/services.html) / [services_cn.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/zeta/services_cn.html)
- [portfolio.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/zeta/portfolio.html) / [portfolio_cn.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/zeta/portfolio_cn.html)
- etc...

### 4. Technical Elevation (Japanese Precision V5)
- **Glassmorphism**: Subtle frosted-glass panels in the Services and Contact sections.
- **Micro-Interactions**: Smooth scroll reveals and hover state transitions.
- **Mobile First**: Fully responsive layouts for all devices.

